** TSU
0123456789
** ER
E-01 A FACTORY CORD IS NOT INPUT
E-02 PLEASE INPUT THE FACTORY CORD WITH A NUMBER
E-03 A RATHER THIN MASTER DOES NOT HAVE A FACTORY CORD
E-04 A PROCESS CORD IS NOT INPUT
E-05 A PROCESS NAME MASTER DOES NOT HAVE A PROCESS CORD
E-06 A PART MASTER DOES NOT HAVE A REPRESENTATIVE ARTICLE NUMBER
E-07 THERE ARE NOT DATA TO INQUIRE ABOUT
